Heat oven to 450 degrees F. Cut chicken into bite-sized pieces. Melt Saute Express(R) square in 10-inch nonstick skillet over medium-low heat just until bubbles begin to form. Add chicken. Saute 4-5 minutes or until chicken is done. Spread peanut sauce over pizza crust. Top with broccoli slaw, green onions, cheese and chicken. Place pizza directly on oven rack. Bake 10-12 minutes or until cheese is melted. Top with cilantro and peanuts.